data.description: This well-cared for 'TREE STREETS" cottage is back on the market - no fault of the home!  Its classic charm is evident in the beautifully refinished hardwood floors and the preserved architectural details of its era. Natural light floods every corner, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The kitchen has been thoughtfully updated with brand-new stainless steel appliances, ensuring modern convenience while maintaining the home's timeless character. From the welcoming entryway to the lower-level bonus room, full bedroom with an egress window, and the newly remodeled tiled bathroom, every corner exudes beauty and comfort. Mature trees gracefully line the lot, and the backyard is a private, cozy retreat that feels like an additional room, perfect for relaxation and enjoyment. Additional perks include a new furnace, ample closet space, fresh carpet and paint throughout.
